    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "Twelve of thirteen V&V 40 credibility factors meet or exceed their required levels. The single deficient factor (Test conditions, achieved Gradation 2 vs. required Gradation 3) is acknowledged; the limitation is mitigated by the high consistency of results across three independent modeling teams and two independent test laboratories, and by a sensitivity analysis demonstrating < 3% QoI variation over the clinically plausible angulation range. The overall credibility evidence is sufficient to support the Medium assurance level for this Class II device submission.",
